Prague is an old and charming city and to fully engage with its beauty you only need you feet and a few tips about where to start. 


Prague is an old and charming city. It has more than a million inhabitants, it lies on the large meadreds of the river Vltava, its roofs are red and its streets are narrow, and it doesn't only have a hundred of spires but also hundreds of great deeds and gripping tales stored in its historical posession.
